reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 28, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Best Brand I Have Used!
reviews.reviewText: I recently purchased the Smart Devil Tempered Glass iPhone 13 Protector for my new iPhone, and I must say, I am extremely impressed with its performance!First and foremost, installation was a breeze. The package came with everything I needed, including a cleaning kit and clear instructions. Within minutes, I had the protector flawlessly attached to my phone without any bubbles or imperfections. It fit perfectly and didn't hinder the functionality of the device at all.The quality of this tempered glass protector is outstanding. It feels durable and sturdy, providing excellent protection against scratches, smudges, and even accidental drops. The edges are precisely cut, ensuring a smooth and seamless touch experience. Moreover, the clarity of the glass is remarkable, preserving the original screen quality while adding an extra layer of protection.I particularly appreciate the oleophobic coating on the surface, which helps to repel fingerprints and smudges, making it easy to keep my screen clean and clear. The touch sensitivity remains unaffected, and I have not experienced any loss in responsiveness since applying the protector.Another noteworthy feature is the precise cutouts for the front-facing camera, speaker, and sensors. The protector does not interfere with the Face ID functionality, ensuring that facial recognition works flawlessly.In terms of durability, the Smart Devil Tempered Glass iPhone 13 Protector has exceeded my expectations. The protector has endured daily wear and tear without any signs of chipping or cracking. I feel confident that it will provide long-lasting protection for my iPhone.Overall, I highly recommend the Smart Devil Tempered Glass iPhone 13 Protector to anyone looking for reliable and high-quality screen protection. It offers excellent durability, crystal-clear visibility, and a seamless touch experience. This protector is a worthy investment to safeguard your valuable iPhone 13 from scratches and accidental damage.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 2, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Is a great deal.
reviews.reviewText: Package arrived quickly and in perfect condition. The written installation instructions are easy to follow. You do have to remove the case the iPhone is in before you can use and install the screen protector guide. Followed the instructions and ended up with a perfectly fitting screen protector. Initially I did have a couple of small "bubbles" in the glass, but was able to work one out and the other disappeared after the phone was used and the screen warmed up. There was no change in the touch or sight of the phone. Works and looks perfectly on my iPhone 15. It does slow down fingerprints also.

reviews.reviewText: I have used many different screen protectors over the years and, for the most part, they are all about the same. The best part of this one is the ease of installation. The frame that it comes with snaps over your phone and creates perfect alignment. All you have to do is place the glass inside the frame and let go. The glass almost installs itself! Perfect alignment and no bubbles!! Excellent product.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United Kingdom on January 29, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: Didn’t know I could feel this passionately about a screen protector
reviews.reviewText: So I never review anything ever but I had to leave a review on this because I will never be buying a different screen protector ever. It’s SO conveniently packaged so that you don’t have stickers and cloths and all sorts falling out the box like other screen protectors, and everything has a numbered step on it so you couldn’t possibly get this wrong!The screen protector itself went on ridiculously easy and adhered itself with one light swipe down the centre with absolutely 0 air bubbles, and as someone who bought this product in frustration after spending a good half an hour trying to get a screen protector on without a million air bubbles I’m completely in love. Now that it’s on my phone I completely forget that it’s there, it looks so seamless and feels absolutely AMAZING.Never felt quite so enthused by protective phone materials before but it’s honestly made my day (tbf it has been a rather rubbish day but I’m sure it would have made my day regardless!)
